adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f59e93678d2e5bcc7e240ba585092395ba34ba57","tid":1219304,"uid":215905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:13:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd0c2d88465ced8380069026cd687b1a0acbed5","tid":1219304,"uid":215905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:13:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d98bf54b9ac30d20ff4b1b00f4497144747767","tid":1219304,"uid":216874,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/iI0umujg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FiI0umujg.jpg&h=285a4ec9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d20bf49013f6fbf49018cc9c99778ad02289110f","tid":1219304,"uid":110259,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:16:14.000Z","msg":"各位不如幫手同身邊支持解釋下全件事先<br />\n我知聽落好d難，但有唔少睇開報紙個堆其實真係唔知修例內容，重點係同佢地用道理講番清楚全件事，特別依家開始各有各做，我地需要製造更多輿論壓力，哪怕5分鐘都好，一百萬人每人說服到兩個人，就已經多二百萬人架啦，更何況每日講既話呢。對屋企人既，今次用返人權角度同佢地講番清楚修例既問題係邊，話d人倒亂既，同佢解釋返議會失衡既，已經冇任何正規溝通方式，777一意孤行既事。<br />\n講唔關佢事既但有樓既，俾石禮謙攤訂單野俾佢睇，同佢解釋對樓市個d有咩影響。<br />\n對返緊工儲緊錢或者對退左休既，同佢解釋如果條例通過佢儲蓄會變廢紙既事<br />\n對話支持中國既，俾返佢睇中國有簽人權法案，大陸自稱支持人權而且一直良好，問下講話支持中國又支持政府既佢地係咪反中央政府，同佢解釋一國兩制，再俾環球時報之前個篇野俾佢睇，用各種說法去駁佢地講既野，因為通常佢地講既都係空洞說話。<br />\n講支持警察既，盡量講番警察犯左既野係警察自己set既野。<br />\n如果唔明點解人權凌駕法律既，解釋全件事俾佢聽啦。<br />\n總之哪怕用咩方式說服都好，道理係我地個邊，冇一個法律體系可以凌駕於人權，即係人既自然權利，每日用5分鐘至十分鐘，再加少少說服技巧，影響力已經大好多。我知要同佢地溝通好難，但佢地好多既都係人講咩佢講咩。我懇請大家幫手製造輿論，哪怕每日每人身邊說服幾個，條例會比之前更難通過。我地需要係所有方面都下手，求求大家幫手。"},{"pid":"7fd6d0c8e8729f4f5c8ca5f184a01693b313a752","tid":1219304,"uid":215905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:18:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da274f86b2471b89bb3c93d21f16879184b55ff2","tid":1219304,"uid":84367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:19:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"869ad6bf5039ce8b2a2b4807e470c364fc061351","tid":1219304,"uid":215905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:22:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"087ac58ec63e1fa549013d099d8291dd01f57602","tid":1219304,"uid":215905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:22:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"586